  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Response to humanitarian emergency in Afghanistan caused by political instability, drought and unusually cold winter. Activities will include: 

- distribution of WASH kits to HH in 5 provinces 

- Cash assistance for winterisation support (for fuel, blankets etc.)

- MHPSS activities and establishing a safe space for women and girls in Bamyan

- Cash support for livelihoods 

- Cash support for food</narrative>
  </description>
